import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1):
    v0 = jnp.maximum(x0, x1)
    v1 = jnp.tanh(v0)
    v2 = jnp.multiply(x0, v1)
    v3 = jnp.add(v0, v1)
    v4 = jnp.maximum(v3, x1)
    v5 = jnp.exp(v1)
    v6 = jnp.multiply(v0, v5)
    v7 = jnp.tanh(v4)
    v8 = jnp.add(v0, v5)
    v9 = jnp.tanh(v8)
    return v9
